We need to show:
`∀ f hf, eLpNorm (T f) 1 (ν.restrict G) ≤ (4 * c / p) * eLorentzNorm f p 1 μ * (ν G) ^ p'⁻¹.toReal`

The proof strategy is to use the fact that any complex function `f` can be decomposed into four non-negative real functions:
