/- The main theorem states that if an operator T satisfies the restricted weak type condition, then it also satisfies the Lorentz type condition. -/
theorem HasRestrictedWeakType.hasLorentzType [TopologicalSpace α] {𝕂 : Type*} /- [MeasurableSpace ε'] [BorelSpace ε'] -/
